{"tid":57333,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米手機著火 賠償前要先簽收聲協議","createTime":"2016-12-28T02:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T13:48:10.000Z","uid":55951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb24d10f5cdf0070f617e09f6b29105198d3ddc","tid":57333,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:11:49.000Z","msg":"報導指受害者的小米手機在今年 3 月購買，送給女兒作為禮物，至今未過一年保養期。在冬至當天手機在充電期間忽然發出高熱，縱使馬上從充電器拔除，用戶依然被灼傷。用戶當時使用的充電器和 USB 線均屬原裝，亦未有一邊充電一邊使用手機。在聯絡客戶服務部後，小米開始對事件進行調查，經過商討之後，小米決定向受害者全數退款，並且給予人民幣 600 元作補償。<br />\n<br />\n要取得小米的賠償，受害人需要簽署保密協議，禁止向傳媒公開事件，亦不可以在社交平台或其他渠道公開。如果拒絕簽署的話，則不可以獲得分文賠償。受害人最後簽了協議，但律師表明條款不合法，所以最後將事件曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/12/28/xiaomi-victim-forced-to-sign-nda/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2Fxiaomi-victim-forced-to-sign-nda%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=NZ7uMZVkKH4XTvpQbMBpr2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=670d833c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/12/28/xiaomi-victim-forced-to-sign-nda/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"2e0d486c4e25ea6e920b60cc81c86bb2c7ea742b","tid":57333,"uid":839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:41:17.000Z","msg":"符合蟈蜻"},{"pid":"90a3480b0e8b21102ac2e4690bd4f20f90cd02af","tid":57333,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"600蚊掩口費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3e17aad2243e88bd55ad27f2f41998a6ff8eda","tid":57333,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"燒唔撚死理應偷笑 六百蚊當獎金啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca9d0a7963e6b8a4fb448138f26ecfe15526c1e","tid":57333,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:48:01.000Z","msg":"還有党呀"},{"pid":"52d286921cbc3eea8a6829e8f5e451d4a1f93d1b","tid":57333,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci